article_id:336,category_name:News,title_name:Issue Regarding Data Display,image_path:,message:<div>Following the March 18 maintenance, we have confirmed cases where there was a gap between some of the data shown on screen and the actual data (such as remaining stamina or getherwing numbers).</div><div><br></div><div>This could cause the following issues:</div><div>・A &quot;Support code: 99999&quot; error being displayed and the game going back to the title screen.</div><div>・The numbers for resources such as stamina, getherwings, mana, rupies, etc. changing suddenly when the actual data was being reflected.</div><div>Note: This was merely a result of the actual data being reflected in the game, so there was no actual loss or gain of said resources.</div><div><br></div><div>This issue has now been fixed.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1553850000,update_time1553853301